\begin_layout Standard
We did Rand index analysis for cross subject comparison as well as cross
 session analysis.
 For cross subject analysis, for a given clustering algorithm and given
 connectivity measure, we computed pairwise Rand indices for each pair of
 subject.
 These rand indices were averaged over all the subjects and sessions.
 Conversely, for cross session Rand analysis, for a given clustering algorithm
 and given connectivity measure, we computed pairwise Rand indices for all
 pairs of sessions for each subject.
 These rand indices were again averaged over all the subjects and sessions.
\end_layout

